Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.32,0:06:19.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His only living relatives were his two daughters Ryoko and Keiko
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.62,0:06:23.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He seems to have left a will saying that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:27.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he would leave his entire estate to Ryoko who had taken a husband
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:28.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I 888...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.97,0:06:30.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so if Ryoko disappears,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.00,0:06:35.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the estate that she originally couldn't inherit would be hers...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:36.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.21,0:06:39.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because there was nothing on the death note that said,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:42.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,if the younger sister dies, don-t7give it to the older sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.11,0:06:43.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.05,0:06:44.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ryoko's husband is clean!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:48.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If his wife dies he loses the estate and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:52.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No... not really so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.62,0:06:55.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her husband Akira\NMorozumi is a psychiatrist,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.23,0:06:57.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and wanted to demolish that house
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.53,0:06:59.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that they were living in and build his own hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.13,0:07:03.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But since Ryoko was opposed to it, he seems to have been in a fix...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.35,0:07:08.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He seems to have been given that land and house by Ryoko's parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.67,0:07:13.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On top of that, if he knew that his wife was having an extra-maritalzaffair,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.58,0:07:15.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he would have more than enough motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:19.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The problem is all three of them have an alibi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:21.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.42,0:07:25.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the time the arsonist set fire and put this horse at the site was around 7:30 pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:30.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her husband came home about 10 minutes before that but,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.49,0:07:33.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,after that before even a minute had passed,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:36.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he went out drinking with the Sensei of Feng Shu
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.57,0:07:38.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And at that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.17,0:07:42.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the fortune-teller was telling fortunes in a building in front of Haido:Station... =~.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.74,0:07:46.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the only suspect left is
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.81,0:07:50.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the-man who was at the front door of
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.08,0:07:52.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the Morozumi residence when we got there...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.62,0:07:55.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The man who tried to leave the catalog of the things in his store and
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:07:58.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,key holder that would help business prosper.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.75,0:08:00.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But was asked to leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:04.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The owner of the antique store, at timid looking man...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:08.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unless we can figure out who and where he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.40,0:08:13.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder what this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.27,0:08:16.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, this horse that was found at the first fire site?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.27,0:08:18.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only this horse has a strange protrusion on its body!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.84,0:08:21.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't this the feet of a, human?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.74,0:08:24.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's melted from the heat of the fire but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.38,0:08:26.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe somebody was mounted on this horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.68,0:08:29.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The military commander that was riding the Red Rabbit Horse was,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.55,0:08:30.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,who was he...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.69,0:08:34.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,K-Kanu!
