Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.48,0:08:56.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't have time to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.15,0:08:59.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's call all the antique shops in the vicinity of Haidocho!
