Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.08,0:09:37.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although it didn't seem to work last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.39,0:09:42.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to wish with all my might tonight so that it works!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.46,0:09:43.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.49,0:09:50.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've found them. I've finally found them...
