Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:24.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His father used to be a firefighter, and when he was still in elementary school,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.63,0:10:28.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,his father tried to save a person who couldn't make it out of the fire'in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:30.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And was swallowed by the flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:32.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Don't tell me that the man 1s .
