Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.43,0:18:57.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,with the fortune Ã©ller KeikoGondo too...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.80,0:19:00.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. I haven't gone that far yet, but...
