Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.23,0:19:08.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Ryoko was found, I saw her gripping this small cushion really hard .
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.07,0:19:11.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had them all come this morning to headquarters and asked them
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:14.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,if this looked familiar to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.25,0:19:19.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but only that woman Gondo turned pale and left in the wink of an eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.02,0:19:22.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that a dying messagej?
