Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.86,0:19:26.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The arsonist had already confessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.53,0:19:30.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that lady already had an alibi\Nso we couldn't detain her...
