Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:37.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, would you like to confirm for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.64,0:19:40.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who testified is the boy next door...
