Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.64,0:19:47.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:49.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the opening song of Kamen Yaiba started
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.82,0:19:53.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw a large shadow of a horse on the curtain of the living room!
