Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.72,0:20:01.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because I entered the living room at 7:30 ind turned on the lights right away...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.79,0:20:03.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I'm not sure if there was a shadow there or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.46,0:20:05.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying!
