Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.84,0:20:14.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:17.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The shadow of the horse was projected on this curtain...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.85,0:20:22.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,True...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.92,0:20:23.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,True...
