Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.56,0:20:33.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's like watching a movie and really cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:37.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But sonny... make sure you turn on the'lights whenfyou watch TV. okay!
