Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.13,0:20:41.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.90,0:20:49.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe the shadow of the horse was already projected before 7:30...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.41,0:20:55.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The shadow that is createdyby flames get light and dark and sways a lot too, so
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.41,0:20:58.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you can't tell if it's a horse or not at times.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:21:00.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.99,0:21:04.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because I was watching baseball all the while
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.22,0:21:07.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,until the clock on top of the TV struck the time for Kamen Yaiba but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.26,0:21:10.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It got really bright outside the window and I saw the shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.86,0:21:13.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was time for the Kamen Yaiba song.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.13,0:21:16.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'Hen were you watching the baseball game with the room dark too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.90,0:21:21.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But; if it's dark you can't see the time of the clock, right...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.51,0:21:25.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could see it because it was dimly light outside the window...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.25,0:21:30.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, the shadow of the horse wasn't swaying.
