Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.52,0:21:36.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.29,0:21:39.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look really closely for it Hattori!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.06,0:21:40.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it's somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.83,0:21:41.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.71,0:21:44.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The evidence that will prove our deduction, is here some place for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.30,0:21:46.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.43,0:21:48.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's an incandescent electric light bulb!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.40,0:21:51.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've found one here too!
